    note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port
    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller target<br/>against InferencePool pod allowlist
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed (or 403 Forbidden)

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>+ kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: KV transfer metadata<br/>(kv_transfer_params response)

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>+ kv_transfer_params from prefiller<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
    Decoder-->>Client: Inference Response<br/>(streamed via sidecar)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefiller Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward request directly<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)
    Decoder-->>Client: Inference Response<br/>(streamed via sidecar)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    note over Allowlist,Prefiller: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Updates (Background)

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Allowlist->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool + Pods<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Allowlist: Watch stream updates<br/>(30s resync interval)
